{"title":"生命的长城——“八一”抒怀","authors":["吴其辉"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":7,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“八一”抒怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴其辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在万里长城内外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一座绿色的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不是防风林带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比防风林更无畏更坚定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它能承当突降的恶雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也能制服来袭的暴风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在万里长城内外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一座生命的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光给了它鲜活的色泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民给了它常青的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪口上的准星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这长城的堞口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城的肩膀上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托起对祖国的全部忠诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长城属于古老的过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这生命的长城啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于神州的希望与永恒"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}